{"tid":108274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"+ [有情有義]唔只澳門 澳洲也會受支爆波及!?","createTime":"2017-02-05T06:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T10:41:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d37f7a1214506af65c9ced23c231c9fed84c9d3","tid":108274,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>我死朱振華</strong><br />\n今天 01:29 <br />\n<br />\n澳大利亞這次陪著贏國跳崖的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong>@快蘭斯24小時財經直播</strong><br />\n<br />\n實時播報：【阿里巴巴設澳新總部 馬雲用行動力挺全球化】<br />\n<br />\n北京時間2月4日，阿里巴巴集團澳大利亞新西蘭總部揭幕典禮在澳大利亞新南威爾士州舉行。<br />\n典禮上，浙商總會會長、阿里巴巴集團董事局主席馬雲表示，要將「讓天下沒有難做的生意」的理念帶到大洋洲。<br />\n他也指出，世界需要全球化和貿易，應該用商業和信任連接世界。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"34d9ed42ecb942d1f2d70cd191219cf740583dce","tid":108274,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:45:00.000Z","msg":"為什麼<br />\n今天 01:46<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我死朱振華：澳洲成功躲過1998年的東南亞經濟危機靠的是贏國的鐵礦石採購。<br />\n用鐵礦石訂單生出來的貨幣量哦！<br />\n這十幾年間的貨幣量發行巨大。<br />\n<br />\n贏國鋼鐵過剩，一部分原因也是鐵礦石貿易訂單不能違約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n現在鋼鐵出口將被完全幹掉。那麼新增外匯無法獲得，採購用的錢怎麼辦？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">違約意味著澳洲鐵礦石抵押物貶值，澳洲的銀行呢？<br />\n</span>今天 02:46"},{"pid":"06380e7e12fc4cd7dddd8d0e3c00d580dbcf4f34","tid":108274,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://wx1.sinaimg.cn/mw1024/3defed62gy1fcffjedqo3j20qo1betp4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw1024%2F3defed62gy1fcffjedqo3j20qo1betp4.jpg&h=bc7f21d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://wx1.sinaimg.cn/mw1024/3defed62gy1fcffj63913j20qo1bencv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw1024%2F3defed62gy1fcffj63913j20qo1bencv.jpg&h=1bee7e81&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n有兩張圖片可以很好的補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今天 11:25"},{"pid":"dc95e81458cd3e2955efd754896387e0ab693136","tid":108274,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:46:21.000Z","msg":"同樣指靠中國貿易 同樣大量中國熱錢 同樣地產泡沫 新西蘭也一塊唄<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/74/moren_hashiqi_org.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.t.sinajs.cn%2Ft4%2Fappstyle%2Fexpression%2Fext%2Fnormal%2F74%2Fmoren_hashiqi_org.png&h=aeec1107&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n今天 03:11 <br />\n<br />\n跳崖後會摔成什麼樣，多久能站起來??? <br />\n今天 04:41 <br />\n<br />\n歡迎跳崖！ <br />\n今天 05:26"},{"pid":"cffeaf70583baee0f25673d2b080498ed071a5c2","tid":108274,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:46:43.000Z","msg":"澳洲物價真是虛高，感覺澳幣應該貶值。澳洲銀行風險增加，不知道會到倒閉的程度嗎 <br />\n今天 04:38"},{"pid":"678c96a13587f5bd9ca5fb56acebc2b8a33f3626","tid":108274,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}